[
    {
        "text": "I hid behind a big tree that was knocked down or fallen.",
        "startTime": 4333,
        "endTime": 9171,
        "slowStartTime": 6650,
        "slowEndTime": 13981
    },
    {
        "text": "And I could see these Germans in the woods across this big field.",
        "startTime": 10291,
        "endTime": 16507,
        "slowStartTime": 15587,
        "slowEndTime": 24986
    },
    {
        "text": "And I saw this young kid crawling up a ditch straight towards my tree.",
        "startTime": 17042,
        "endTime": 25014,
        "slowStartTime": 25713,
        "slowEndTime": 37746
    },
    {
        "text": "So, I let him crawl. I didn't fire at him.",
        "startTime": 26412,
        "endTime": 29838,
        "slowStartTime": 39768,
        "slowEndTime": 44982
    },
    {
        "text": "But when he got up within three or four foot of me,...",
        "startTime": 30514,
        "endTime": 35251,
        "slowStartTime": 45921,
        "slowEndTime": 53101
    },
    {
        "text": "...I screamed at him to surrender.",
        "startTime": 35496,
        "endTime": 39560,
        "slowStartTime": 53394,
        "slowEndTime": 59565
    },
    {
        "text": "And instead of surrendering, he started to pull his gun towards me...",
        "startTime": 40240,
        "endTime": 45725,
        "slowStartTime": 60510,
        "slowEndTime": 68813
    },
    {
        "text": "...which was instant death for him.",
        "startTime": 46272,
        "endTime": 48824,
        "slowStartTime": 69558,
        "slowEndTime": 73461
    },
    {
        "text": "But this young man, he was blonde, blue eyes, fair-skinned, so handsome.",
        "startTime": 50247,
        "endTime": 58599,
        "slowStartTime": 75520,
        "slowEndTime": 88124
    },
    {
        "text": "He was like a little angel but I still had to shoot him.",
        "startTime": 58968,
        "endTime": 63823,
        "slowStartTime": 88602,
        "slowEndTime": 95960
    },
    {
        "text": "And it didn't bother me the first night...",
        "startTime": 65031,
        "endTime": 68665,
        "slowStartTime": 97696,
        "slowEndTime": 103222
    },
    {
        "text": "...because I went to sleep and I was so tired.",
        "startTime": 69206,
        "endTime": 73533,
        "slowStartTime": 103959,
        "slowEndTime": 110524
    },
    {
        "text": "But the second night, I woke up crying because that kid was dead.",
        "startTime": 73657,
        "endTime": 83401,
        "slowStartTime": 110635,
        "slowEndTime": 125326
    },
    {
        "text": "And to this day, I wake up many nights crying.",
        "startTime": 85791,
        "endTime": 91615,
        "slowStartTime": 128836,
        "slowEndTime": 137648
    },
    {
        "text": "I still see him in my dreams.",
        "startTime": 92895,
        "endTime": 95835,
        "slowStartTime": 139492,
        "slowEndTime": 143978
    },
    {
        "text": "And I don't know how to get him off my mind.",
        "startTime": 97294,
        "endTime": 101702,
        "slowStartTime": 146091,
        "slowEndTime": 152778
    }
]